data.title: College Announces Spring Honor Roll
data.meta_description: Wake Tech President Dr. Scott Ralls is proud to announce 2,092 students made the Honor Roll for the Spring 2024 semester.
data.text:
RALEIGH, N.C. (May 29, 2024) â€“ Wake Tech President Dr. Scott Ralls is proud to announce 2,092 students made the Honor Roll for the Spring 2024 semester.

The 855 full-time students who earned a place on the President's List maintained a grade point average (GPA) of 4.0. The 1,237 full-time students who made the Dean's List maintained a GPA of at least 3.5.

The Honor Roll recognizes full-time students with a minimum of 12 credit hours in degree programs.
